summary: A small player room for starting characters.
descriptionHtml:
[center][heading][b][size=14][color=#3174d2]Hole in the Wall - Windhelm[/color][/size][/b][/heading]
[img]http://i1079.photobucket.com/albums/w503/ytnam/Skyrim/Hole%20in%20the%20Wall%20-%20Windhelm/Windhelmbridge.jpg[/img][/center]A player room with a small amount of storage and an alchemist's table, inside the Windhelm bridge.
Designed for starting new characters, just a small base until you find your feet.
Minimal storage (all safe) and alchemy, with cooking available inside.
All smithing stations and wood chopping available just inside the gates!
Comes with free Windhelm guards!
